 <name>Jami</name>
 <summary>Privacy oriented voice, video, chat and conference platform</summary>
 <icon type="stock">jami</icon>
 <description>
    <p>
      A secure and distributed voice, video and chat communication platform
      that requires no centralized server and leaves the power of privacy in the
      hands of users.
    </p>
    <p>
      Jami supports the following key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>One to one conversations</li>
      <li>Share files</li>
      <li>Audio calls</li>
      <li>Audio conferences</li>
      <li>Video calls</li>
      <li>Video conferences</li>
      <li>Share screen in video calls and conferences</li>
      <li>Leave audio messages</li>
      <li>Leave video messages</li>
      <li>End-to-end encryption</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      It can also serve as a SIP software phone.
    </p>
    <p>
      Clients for Windows, macOS, iPhone and Android are available and make Jami
      interoperable.
    </p>
 </description>

